Insider Activity


Individual




Mark D. Millett



Mr. Mark D. Millett is President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Steel Dynamics, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Steel Dynamics, Inc.
Mr. Millett was previously employed as President & Chief Operating Officer by OmniSource Corp., Executive VP-Flat Rolled Steel Operations by The Techs, Chief Metallurgist by NUCLEAR CORP OF AMERICA INC, and Executive Vice President-Metals Recycling by Ferrous Resources Ltd.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Surrey.



