Mark D. Millett 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Executive Officer at STEEL DYNAMICS INC, Mark D. Millett  made $6,563,182 in total compensation.  Of this total $1,010,000 was received as a salary, $2,525,000 was received as a bonus, $383,040 was received in stock options, $2,609,140 was awarded as stock and $36,002 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


