Mark Millett serves as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Steel Dynamics Inc., the Fort Wayne, Indiana-based company he helped found in 1993 - with a little financial help from Mitt Romney and Bain Capital. Millett was appointed to the post in January 2012 after less than a year of serving as President and Chief Operating Off 
